left"><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px">🌟 Jai Jinendra,<span th:text="${firstName}"></span>! 🌟</p><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px">Your Profile is under review by our admin team! You will get email updates once your profile is approved. 📬</p><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:10px">Welcome to Jain Jagruti Centre, USA (JJC USA). JJC USA, a branch of Jain Jagruti Centre Central Board & Charitable Trust, is a non-profit organization formed in 2019. It is formed by a group of volunteers dedicated towards implementing diverse initiatives that contribute to the overall upliftment of its members. 🌍</p><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px">We are a growing organization of 1200+ Jain students and working professionals in the US. We are building a platform with the primary purpose of helping Jain students and working professionals in the United States with the aim to provide: 📚</p><span style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0">These include:</span><ul style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:25px"><li>Opportunities for networking 🤝</li><li>Support individuals’ professional & career growth 🚀</li><li>Assist them in building a strong community 👥</li></ul><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px">We have 5 pillars that function together to support our member community. 💪</p><span style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0">They are:</span><ul style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:25px"><li>Alumni Welfare Committee 🎓</li><li>Student Welfare Committee 📚</li><li>Social Events Committee 🎉</li><li>Website Development 💻</li><li>Marketing and Communication 📢</li></ul><p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px">To stay connected and interact with our members